author: al-Qabīsī, Abu al-Saqr ʿAbd al-ʿAzīz ibn ʿUthmān, fl. 980
title: Precla[rum] summi in astro[rum] scientia principis / Alchabitij opus ad scrutanda stellarum magisteria isagogicum pristino candori nuperrime restitutum ab ... Antonio de Fantis Tarvisino, qui notabilem eiusdem auctoris libellum de planetarum coniunctionib
